                        <interp inst="t18450616-name-109" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES VIVIAN</persName>
                  </hi>. I was in King Edward-street, and saw the prisoner handing the handkerchief back to the prosecutor—I had not seen him be<lb></lb>fore then—I fetched the policeman.</p>
